’Щ@04c2e76b10a81e6615466accd4325b1e502d691560a94c5d45568b20432428d2ЪаTitle: title: bytes add
Path: Examples
Content:
Add bytes 
``0x[AA]``
 to 
``0x[1F FF AA AA]``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AA] | bytes add 0x[AA]
Length: 5 (0x5) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   aa 1f ff aa  aa                                      Г—вЂўГ—Г—Г—


```
Add bytes 
``0x[AA BB]``
 to 
``0x[1F FF AA AA]``
 at index 1.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AA] | bytes add 0x[AA BB] --index 1
Length: 6 (0x6) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   1f aa bb ff  aa aa                                   вЂўГ—Г—Г—Г—Г—


```
Add bytes 
``0x[11]``
 to 
``0x[FF AA AA]``
 at the end.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[FF AA AA] | bytes add 0x[11] --end
Length: 4 (0x4) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   ff aa aa 11                                          Г—Г—Г—вЂў


```
Add bytes 
``0x[11 22 33]``
 to 
``0x[FF AA AA]``
 at the end, at index 1(the index is start from end).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[FF AA BB] | bytes add 0x[11 22 33] --end --index 1
Length: 6 (0x6) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   ff aa 11 22  33 bb                                   Г—Г—вЂў"3Г—


```
